description:
The Dominion of Phezzan was an autonomous region within the http://anidb.net/ch95944 [Galactic Empire], a planet-state within the Phezzan Corridor, which was able to serve as a neutral party in the Allianceâ€“Imperial War by facilitating trade between the Empire and http://anidb.net/ch95945 [Free Planets Alliance]. By the reign of Kaiser http://anidb.net/ch206 [Friedrich IV], the Dominion of Phezzan had become an economic superpower. Its flag was the two headed eagle crest of the Goldenbaum Dynasty rendered in silver, over a yellow triangle and black background.
Source: Gineipaedia
